d)  \n  \n [CWinApp](../../mfc/reference/cwinapp-class.md)  \n  \n `COleControlModule`  \n  \n## Requirements  \n **Header:** afxctl.h  \n  \n## See Also  \n [MFC Sample TESTHELP](../../visual-cpp-samples.md)   \n [Hierarchy Chart](../../mfc/hierarchy-chart.md)\n\n\n\n"}